description:
These metal stainless steel permanent cage nuts are securely screwed into place on round rails to ensure your investment in valuable rack-mountable tech stays protected from all side forces.

Need to mount that giant server cabinet securely to the rack? Installing a new processor for your enterprise-level computer?

Make sure your expensive rack-mountable equipment is secure and installed with a tight fit using stainless steel cage nuts. This product is designed to provide greater stability, security, and increase the lifetime of any server cabinet or environment that uses these special screws.
